Né-ɔɔ́ mɛ̌hɔ̄b békúdé mɔ́, ńtɛ̄dē mɔ́, ákag.”
44-45 Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́ bǐn bémbɛ̄ dyam kəd. Etondɛɛ andím, ehíntɛ́n ékwɛ̄-ʼɛ ekíde áte ésyə̄ə̄l kə́ə́ŋ ne á ngə́ŋ éláán. Abad áde dênkǎb Ndáb-e-Dyǒb áte dênsalé áte eʼpɛd éʼbɛ.
Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ ásɛdtɛɛ́ bɔ́ aáken, “Mekan méhéé mɛ̂?” Boŋ bélāŋgē mɔ́ bán, “Mekan ḿme mébɛ́nlédé tə̂ŋgɛne Yesuɛ, mod a Nazarɛt. Ambɛ́ nkal éʼdəə́dəŋ awě ahɔ́béʼáá, ábɛlé-ʼɛ ndəle é mekan áʼsō éʼ Dyǒb ne áʼsō éʼ baányoŋ.
Mměn mɛ̌lōmē nyé chǒm éche Titɛ́ɛ ánhɔ̄bpē aá mɔ́ɔ̄lōmē nyé. Boŋ nyélyəg nyédyɛɛ á dyad-tê kə́ə́ŋ né nyêkudé ene ngíne echě ebíde ámīn.”
Bɔɔb-pɔɔ́ Befarisia bɔ́ɔ bénlōm ábê bad ábe bémpɛ̌ wɛ́ɛ Jɔnɛ.
Mǐm mêmmaá áte. Hɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ nyaá ápédé áwē boŋ álāŋgē mɔ́ aá, “Mǐm mémáá bɔ́.”
Nzé epub éhɔ́bé bán chɔ́ étómeʼ, pɛd echě édə́ə́ akɛ chɔ́ɔ ékagké. Ewógeʼ ntɔgag ḿme ébɛlɛɛ́ boŋ weebíɛ́ʼɛ́ wɛ́ɛ ébídɛɛ́ kéʼɛ wɛ́ɛ ékagké. Melemlem nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ édíí ne mod ké ahéé awě achyáádté ne Edəə́dəŋ é Dyǒb.”
(Kénɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ mwěn éedusannaá bad, ábē bembapɛɛ bɔ́ɔ bédúsánnáá bad).
Boŋ Yesuɛ ankwɛntɛ́n bɔ́ aá, “Nwóó ndyééd e adyɛ́ echě nyéēbíiʼɛ́.”
Ábwɔ̄g-ábwɔ̄g ane mod andyɛ̌ bwâm, ányə̄g échē ebúm áte, ábootéd-tɛ akɛ.
Nyéedúbpɛɛ́ ane awě álómé, né-ɔɔ́ nyéēmwagké bán échē eyale édyɛɛ nyé á nlém-tê.
Hɛ́ɛ bétédé mɔ́ á bɔ̌lɛ-tê ne menyiŋge, ábwɔ̄g-ábwɔ̄g bépɛ̄ɛ̄n-nɛ bɔ̌lɛ á nkin wɛ́ɛ békágéʼáá.
Mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé ewɛle éche ébage aloŋgé éche ébídé ádyōb. Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě adyédé échê ewɛle, ǎbɛ̄ á aloŋgé á ngíndé ne á ngíndé. Échɛ́n ewɛle éche mɛ́bɛɛ́ nyé édíi echem yə̌l echě mɛ́bɛ̌ âbɛl boŋ ńkɔde aloŋgé dé nkǒŋsé.”
Ámbīd e póndé áde Yesuɛ baányaŋ bémáá akɛ á Ngande e Eʼbem, mɔ́mpē ankɛ̌ áwed. Boŋ enkênlúmédté yə̌l. Ankɛ̌ nyaa echě bad bénkêmbííʼɛ́ ndín e mod echě ádíí.
Doŋge á bad átîntê ene ndun e mod ábe bénwōg nɛ́ɛ Yesuɛ áhɔ́bɛɛ́ ḿmɛ́n mekan bénhɔ̄b bán, “Ne mbále, anɛ́n mod adíi nkal éʼdəə́dəŋ awě ǎpɛ̌.”
Nɛ́ɛ béhúde ké nɛ̂ áte, á mbéndé echɛ̂n, éténlédé nɛ́n bán nzé bad bébɛ bébídé dyam mbóŋ, boŋ béhɔ́bé melemlem mé dyam, né ene mbóŋ edé mbóŋ e mbále.
Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě ahúú ne Dyǒb, awóge eyale é Dyǒb. Nzɔm echě ekəə́ boŋ nyéewóglán edíi, nyéesaá bǎn bé Dyǒb.”
Ké nɛ̂, bad bé Israɛl bénkêndúbɛ́ɛ́ bán, ane mod ansébé ndím akwɛ. Nɛ̂ dêmbɛ̌l bénchɛ̄lē sáá bɔ́ nyaŋ.
Né-ɔɔ́, Yesuɛ ambád ámpē aá, “Ne mbále, nlâŋge nyé nɛ́n mɛ-ɛɛ́, mɛ́ɛ ndé mmwɛ mé ekob wɛ́ɛ mbód épooʼɛ́.
Nzé meébɛ̄lē nsɔ́n ḿme Titɛ́ɛ, nyéedúbpé mɛ.
Dɔ́ɔ Yesuɛ aláŋgé mɔ́ aá, “Mɛ-ɛɛ́ ndé mpuu né aloŋgé. Nzé mod adúbpé mɛ, ké anwɛ́, ǎbɛ̄ abɛ́ á aloŋgé.
Póndé e ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn embɛ́ bɛnbɛn. Né-ɔɔ́, bad híin bémbīd myad ne myad, békɛ̄ á akuu á Jerusalɛm âwobe échab yə̌l ngáne mbéndé e Mosɛɛ éhɛ́déʼáá, âboŋsɛn ngande e Nnyíme-ámīn.
Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě abɛnle mɛ, atə́ŋgɛ́né awêm mbəledɛ abɛ́. Ké héé-ʼɛ wɛ́ɛ ńdíí, awêm mbəledɛ atə́ŋgɛ́né abɛ́ áhed. Echem Sáŋ ǎbɛ̌-ʼɛ kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě abɛnle mɛ edúbé.
Mbíí mɛɛ́ kéchéé éché áláŋgé mɛ aá ńhɔ̂b épɛɛne aloŋgé áde déemaáʼ. Né-ɔɔ́, kéchéé éche ńhɔ́bɛɛ́, nhɔ́beʼ chɔ́ ngáne Titɛ́ɛ áláŋgé mɛ.”
Áde Judasɛ ákóbé ewɛle éche Yesuɛ ábágé mɔ́ kobɛ́n, ambíd ebwɔ́g. Ehíntɛ́n ênkwɛ̌.
Dɔ́ɔ Judasɛ (saké Judas Iskariɔdɛ) áhɔ́bɛɛ́ aá, “Boŋ A-Sáŋ, chán wɛ́lūmēdtē sé yə̌l boŋ weelúmté nkǒŋsé pɛn?”
Nyéwêmtɛn ehɔ́b éche ménlāāʼɛ́ nyé mɛɛ́ ‘Mbəledɛ eetómɛ́ɛ́ eche sáŋ.’ Nzé bêmbané mɛ á metake-tê né bɛ́bané nyémpē á metake-tê. Nzé bénhīd ádêm ayə́ge né bɛ́hīd-tɛ ádɛ̄n ámpē.
Nɛ̂ dɔ́ɔ édíí ne nyé. Nyêsǔdné bɔɔb, boŋ mɛ̌nyīn nyémpē. Ene póndé ḿmɛn nlém mɛ́lōn ne menyiŋge, modmod éehɛnlé-ʼaá nyé ḿmê menyiŋge akobɛn.
Á etútú échâb membɛ̌ echem yə̌l âbɛle wɛ âbɛl boŋ bɔ́mpē bébɛ échab yə̌l âbɛl boŋ békoŋ wɛ abɛle.
Yesuɛ antimtɛ́n mɔ́ aá, “Nzé nhɔ́bé dyam áde déetə̂ŋgɛne, ehɔ́b dɔ́ moosyəə́l áwôg. Boŋ nzé édé bán nhɔ́bé dyam áde átə́ŋgɛ́né, cheé ékə́ə́ boŋ ébɔmé mɛ?”
Áde Payledɛ áwógé nɛ̂ anhɛ̌d nzii âtɛde Yesuɛ, boŋ ábê bad bénhɛ̄ eʼsaád bán, “Nzé etɛ̌dté anɛ́n mod né weésaá nsón awě Kaisɛɛ. Kénzɛ́ɛ́ awě ahɔ́bé aá, mɔ́dē kə̂ŋ né atə̂ŋgan Kaisɛɛ.”
Ámbīd enɛ̂, Josɛbɛ awě ambíd á dyad á Arimatia, anláá Payledɛ aá, ábɛ mɔ́ kunze âted ndim ḿme Yesuɛ. Josɛbɛ abédɛ́ɛ mbapɛɛ awě Yesuɛ, boŋ énkêmbídédté yə̌l áwed áyə̄le abááʼáá bad bé Israɛl. Payledɛ ambɛ̌ mɔ́ kunze âtéd ndim ḿme Yesuɛ. Né-ɔɔ́, ankɛ̌ Yesuɛ ndim atéd.
Ámbīd e eʼpun waam, bembapɛɛ bênladɛ́n áte á ndáb-te ámpē. Tɔmasɛ mɔ́mpē ambɛ́ áhed. Bêmpěn eʼkob, boŋ Yesuɛ ampɛ̌, atyéém átîntê echâb. Anláá bɔ́ aá, “Nsaŋ ḿbɛ̂ ne nyé.”
Ekud é mam émpēe édé éche Yesuɛ ábɛ́lé. Nzé bénhɔ̄b bán bételeʼ mésyə̄ə̄l ásē, ahɔ́g ámbīd e ádíníí, nwêmtan mɛɛ́ né nkǒŋsé méekwogké échê kálag ahɛ́ áte.
Né-ɔɔ́, bênsǐd mbambú âlúmed bɔ́ mod awě bɛ́pwɛdté. Dɔ́ɔ mbambú élúmté bɔ́ âpwɛd Matiasɛ. Né-ɔɔ́, bémbād Matiasɛ á mesoŋgé mé bembapɛɛ bé nlómag ábíníí dyôm ne nhɔ́g.
